### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:5005/

### Add a batch
POST http://localhost:5005/add_batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ref": "batch-001",
  "sku": "BLUE-CHAIR",
  "qty": 100,
  "eta": "2026-03-15"
}

### Add another batch (earlier ETA)
POST http://localhost:5005/add_batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ref": "batch-002",
  "sku": "BLUE-CHAIR",
  "qty": 50,
  "eta": "2026-03-10"
}

### Allocate an order
POST http://localhost:5005/allocate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderid": "order-123",
  "sku": "BLUE-CHAIR",
  "qty": 10
}

### Try to allocate invalid SKU (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5005/allocate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderid": "order-124",
  "sku": "UNKNOWN-ITEM",
  "qty": 5
}

### Try to allocate too much (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5005/allocate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderid": "order-125",
  "sku": "BLUE-CHAIR",
  "qty": 1000
}